original_title: UFC Fight Night 80: Namajunas vs. VanZant
overview: UFC Fight Night 80: Namajunas vs. VanZant was a mixed martial arts event held on December 10, 2015 at The Chelsea at The Cosmopolitan in Las Vegas, Nevada. The event was headlined by a women's strawweight bout between Paige VanZant and Rose Namajunas.
title: UFC Fight Night 80: Namajunas vs. VanZant
